data.model

Class DataPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.model.DataPoint

  • public class DataPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides an abstract version of points provided by a fitness tracking device. Each dataPoint consists of attributes related to the actual values in the real world at that time point.
    Author:
    Fitr.Team
